#include<iostream>
#include<algorithm>
using namespace std;
int main()
{
    int t;
    cin>>t;
    for(int i=0;i<t;i++)
    {
        int n;
        cin>>n;
        int a[n];
        for(int j=0;j<n;j++)
            cin>>a[j];
            sort(a,a+n);
            int j;
            for(j=0;j<n-1;j++)
                if(a[j]==a[j+1]){
                 cout<<"NO"<<endl;
                    break;
                }
                if(j==n-1)
                    cout<<"YES"<<endl;
    }
    return 0;
}
